trans-unit.source: Interacts with the parser to build the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Współdziała z analizatora do tworzenia <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> formantu.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder"> </xref> klasy.

trans-unit.source: Adds literal content to the control.
trans-unit.target: Dodaje zawartość literalna do formantu.

trans-unit.source: The AppendLiteralString method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder> class overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AppendLiteralString%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class so that the method of the base class has no effect.

trans-unit.source: The literal content to add to the control.
trans-unit.target: Zawartość literalna można dodać do formantu.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the <xref:System.Type> for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control's specified child control.
trans-unit.target: Uzyskuje <xref:System.Type>dla <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> formant użytkownika określony formant podrzędny.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The GetChildControlType method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder> class overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Metoda GetChildControlType <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>klasy zastępuje <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A>metody <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasy.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: This implementation of the GetChildControlType method always returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Ta implementacja metody GetChildControlType zawsze zwraca `null`.

trans-unit.source: The tag name of the child control.
trans-unit.target: Nazwa tagu formantu podrzędnego.

trans-unit.source: An array of attributes contained in the child control.
trans-unit.target: Tablica atrybutów, zawarte w formantu podrzędnego.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType*> method is overridden to always return <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType*>Metoda zostanie przesłonięta do zawsze zwracają <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType*>

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control needs to get its inner text.
trans-unit.target: Określa, czy <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> musi uzyskać wewnętrzny tekst formantu.

trans-unit.source: The NeedsTagInnerText method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder> class overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: Metoda NeedsTagInnerText <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>klasy zastąpienia <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText%2A>metody <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasę, aby zawsze zwracają `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The inner text is the text between the opening and closing tags of the control.
trans-unit.target: Wewnętrzny tekst jest wyświetlany tekst pomiędzy otwierającym, a zamykającym tagiem formantu.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText*> method is overridden to always return <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText*>Metoda zostanie przesłonięta do zawsze zwracają <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText*>

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control's inner text.
trans-unit.target: Ustawia <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> wewnętrzny tekst formantu.

trans-unit.source: This method loads the <xref:System.String> passed in to an XML document to determine whether it is well-formed.
trans-unit.target: Ta metoda ładuje <xref:System.String>przekazany do dokumentu XML, aby ustalić, czy jest poprawnie sformułowany.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: If it is, the code calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli tak jest, kod wywołuje <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A>metody <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasy.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value to insert as the inner text.
trans-unit.target: Wartość, aby wstawić jako tekst wewnętrzny.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.String> object passed in is not well-formed XML.
